cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CV. 

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques for semantic textual similarity. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also uses supervised classification techniques, which falls under the sub-category cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The use of Random Forrest Classifier also suggests the sub-category cs.LG (Learning). The paper also deals with alignment and matching of chunks, which can be related to sub-categories cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.CV (Computer Vision).
